LocalA1Endpoint_nodeCredentialRef__Change causes A1 server restart and takes effect after restart.
LocalA1Endpoint_portNumber__Change causes A1 server restart and takes effect after restart.
LocalA1Endpoint_trustCategoryRef__Change causes A1 server restart and takes effect after restart.

MdtCellProfileUeCfg_m6Enabled__New connection. If M6 is disabled ongoing MDT M6 measurements are stopped at reception of MDT measurement report.
NRCellCU_mdtEnabled__New connection. If MDT is disabled ongoing MDT measurements are stopped at reception of MDT measurement report.
TermPointToAmf_pwsRestartHandling__Next PWS restart or failure message to be transmitted on the NG-C interface. Does not affect ongoing PWS broadcast.

TermPointToENodeB_ipsecEpAddress__Next MO unlock for the change by operator.. Outer IP address received from X2 neighbor node overwrites manual configuration by operator, and manual configuration is ignored.

TermPointToENodeB_upIpAddress__Next MO unlock for the change by operator.. User plan address received from X2 neighbor node overwrites manual configuration by operator, and manual configuration is ignored.
TermPointToGNodeB_ipv4Address__Next MO unlock if changed by operator
TermPointToGNodeB_ipv6Address__Next MO unlock if changed by operator
DataPacketGenerator_duration__Next execution of Downlink Throughput Test in gNodeB.

DataPacketGeneratorUeCfg_prefUeGroupList__Next execution of Downlink Throughput Test in gNodeB.
DataPacketGeneratorUeCfg_ueGroupList__Next execution of Downlink Throughput Test in gNodeB.
CommonBeamforming_coverageShape__For Low-Band and Mid-Band cells, takes effect immediately. For High-Band cells, takes effect at next NRSectorCarrier unlock.
CommonBeamforming_digitalTilt__For Low-Band and Mid-Band sector carriers, takes effect immediately.. For High-Band sector carriers, takes effect at next NRSectorCarrier unlock.
DlOuterLoop_dualOuterLoopEnabled__Immediately for PCell and internal SCell, next cell unlock for external SCell.
DlOuterLoop_initValMixIpn__Immediately for PCell and internal SCell, next cell unlock for external SCell.
DlOuterLoop_initValNonMixIpn__Immediately for PCell and internal SCell, next cell unlock for external SCell.

DlOuterLoop_largeStepNonMixIpn__Immediately for PCell and internal SCell, next cell unlock for external SCell.
DlOuterLoop_smallDownStep__Immediately for PCell and internal SCell, next cell unlock for external SCell.

DynPowerOpt_downUlThreshold__Updated for all UE contexts at next UE connection using configuration from MO instance.
DynPowerOpt_lowDlActivityTimer__Updated for all UE contexts at next UE connection using configuration from MO instance.
DynPowerOpt_lowUlActivityTimer__Updated for all UE contexts at next UE connection using configuration from MO instance.

NRSectorCarrier_txPowerChangeRate__In an unlocked NRSectorCarrier a change will take effect at the next change of txPowerRatio.

NRSectorCarrier_txPowerRatio__If a previous change in txPowerRatio is currently ongoing, the latest change will be started once the previous change has completed. Otherwise the current change will be started immediately.
Paging_defaultPagingCycle__After all the cells in the same gNodeB-DU have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_n__After all the cells in the same gNodeB-DU have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.
Paging_nS__After all the cells in the same gNodeB-DU have been locked, and subsequently been unlocked.

EUtranCellTDD_caPrioThreshold__New connection or next SCell configuration.

EUtranFreqRelation_caFreqProportion__New connection or next SCell configuration.

ExternalGUtranCell_smtcDuration__When X2 link is established. For already established X2 link, at next TermPointToGNB unlock.
ExternalGUtranCell_smtcOffset__When X2 link is established. For already established X2 link, at next TermPointToGNB unlock.
ExternalGUtranCell_smtcPeriodicity__When X2 link is established. For already established X2 link, at next TermPointToGNB unlock.

ReportConfigSCellA1A2_hysteresisA1A2RsrpBidirectional__New connection. Also during ongoing connection, related to next SCell configuration during the connection.

Area_ospfAreaId__All Interface MOs are reconfigured. The OSPFv2 routes from these interfaces are removed from the routing table and traffic is impacted until OSPFv2 has converged.
Interface_interfaceAddress__The Interface MO is reconfigured. The OSPFv2 routes from this interface are removed from the routing table and traffic is impacted until OSPFv2 has converged.

NodeBFunction_eulFachMinAllocation__Next time EulFach is activated (NodeBLocalCell::featCtrlEulFach = ON).

NodeBLocalCell_localCellId__When local cell is idle, i.e. not set up by the RNC.

NodeBLocalCell_maxNumEulUsers__Increase takes effect immediately. Decrease takes gradual effect; existing users are allowed to terminate normally until the new limit is reached. No new users are allowed until below limit.

NodeBLocalCell_maxNumHsPdschCodes__Increase takes effect immediately. Decrease takes effect gracefully (if more codes than the new limit are setup by RNC, the new limit will not apply until the RNC has reconfigured the physical shared channel so that less codes than the new limit are used).

NodeBLocalCell_maxNumHsdpaUsers__Increase takes effect immediately. Decrease takes gradual effect; existing users are allowed to terminate normally until the new limit is reached. No new users are allowed until below limit.
NodeBLocalCell_steeredHsCoreId__NodeBLocalCell::usageState is BUSY (the cell has been setup by the RNC).
NodeBLocalCell_uarfcnDl__At next unlock of Node B Local Cell.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair1__At next unlock of local cell group.
NodeBLocalCellGroup_multiCarrierPair2__At next unlock of local cell group.
